=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_Stethoscope_ex6 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright clean sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 189 Hz, featuring instant attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: instant
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 188.7749
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.3155
  harmonic_regularity: 0.2732
  pitch_clarity: 173.7646
  inharmonicity: 0.4872
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -10.0976
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Stethoscope Example 6
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/Stethoscope.html
// Tags: Stethoscope, Classes, oscillator
// ---
// --- Example 6 ---
(
{ 
    var f = { |l,h| SinOsc.kr(0.1, {pi.rand}).range(l, h) } ;
    Pulse.ar({ f.(20, 1000) }!6, { f.(0.0, 1) }!6, { f.(0.0, 1.0) }!6) 
}.play;
)

c = s.play;
c.numChannels = 6;
c.scopeView.waveColors = [Color.red, Color.red, Color.cyan, Color.cyan, Color.white, Color.white];
c.style = 2;
